                              <h1>
                                    <span>Nous </span>
                                    <span>Contacter</span>
                              </h1>
                              <p><strong>Tél. :</strong> 04 70 42 73 17<br><strong>Fax :</strong> 04 70 42 77 97<br><strong>Mail :</strong> ets.chollet@wanadoo.fr</p>
